      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-cyan-50 border-[3px] border-teal-300 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Unexpected Findings From 47 Nonprofit Website Conversions</h2>
