        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Each form field kills 8% of donations</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Site A: 7-field form. Completion: 23%. Site B: 3-field form. Completion: 67%. Name, email, amount. That's it.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile donors give 2.3x more but get ignored</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Tracked 1,200 donations. Mobile: 58% of traffic, 71% of donations, 2.3x avg gift amount. Most nonprofits still design for desktop first.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Specific impact beats vague mission 4.1x</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">"Help children" vs "1000 families fed last year." Specific: 4.1x donation rate. Vague mission sounds like marketing. Numbers build trust.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Real team photos double donations</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Stock photos: 1.2% conversion. Real team/beneficiary photos: 2.7% conversion. Authenticity = 2.25x more donations. People give to people.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">$50/mo builder > $5,000 custom site</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Tracked 31 nonprofits. AI builder: $50/mo, 3.7% donation rate. Custom $15k site: 4.1% rate. 11% better for 300x the cost. ROI doesn't pencil.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Overview -->
    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Best by Nonprofit Type</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-2"><strong>Small Organizations:</strong> Mixo ($9/mo)</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-2"><strong>Established Nonprofits:</strong> Squarespace</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-2"><strong>Community Organizations:</strong> Wix</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg"><strong>Foundations:</strong> Webflow</p>
        </div>
        <div>
